169
00:13:49,299 --> 00:13:54,299
[SPEAKER_01] Još jedna moja čudna misla

170
00:13:54,299 --> 00:13:56,299
[SPEAKER_01] Mislni eksperiment

171
00:13:56,299 --> 00:14:00,299
[SPEAKER_01] Zamislite neku ženu koja je trudna

172
00:14:00,299 --> 00:14:06,299
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ta žena živi u godini 3000 godina prije Krista

173
00:14:06,299 --> 00:14:12,299
[SPEAKER_01] I sad mi na nekakav magičan način tu ženu teleportiramo u današnje doba

174
00:14:12,299 --> 00:14:21,299
