177
00:14:35,299 --> 00:14:40,299
[SPEAKER_01] Da li bi to djete bilo spremno za svijet kakav je danas?

178
00:14:40,299 --> 00:14:41,299
[SPEAKER_00] To je dobro pitanje

179
00:14:41,299 --> 00:14:48,299
