[SPEAKER_00] 5200

188
00:15:29,299 --> 00:15:31,299
[SPEAKER_00] 52025 godina

189
00:15:31,299 --> 00:15:35,299
[SPEAKER_00] Je cijeli ljudski rod prošao kroz puno toga i to se moralo odraziti na genetiku

190
00:15:35,299 --> 00:15:37,299
